[0.0, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H                                                         \u2502 repo     ananta\n                                                         \u2502 cwd      .\n   \u00b7 \u00b7                                                   \u2502 git      Krusty  main \u2717\n     \u00b7                                                   \u2502 hub      \u25cf localhost:5000\n     \u25c9                                                   \u2502 auth     session_env\n\u25cf  \u25c9 \u25c9                                                   \u2502 section  dashboard\n                                                         \u2502 mode     normal\n                                                         \u2502 \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n[NAV]                  |  DASHBOARD                             |  DETAIL                           \n>! Dashboard           |   ! degraded \u2014 Hub nicht erreichbar... |                                   \n . Goals               |     press r to retry                   |   Commands:                       \n . Tasks               |                                        |     :section <id>   switch section\n . Artifacts           |                                        |     :refresh        reload data   \n . Knowledge           |                                        |     :focus <pane>   nav/content...\n . Config              |                                        |     :help           keybindings   \n . Templates           |                                        |                                   \n . System              |                                        |                                   \n . Audit               |                                        |  CHAT                             \n . Terminal            |                                        |   ACTIVE: #room                   \n . Share / Teilnehmer  |                                        |   [#room] AI notes                \n . Help                |                                        |   ------------------------------  \n                       |                                        |   keine Nachrichten               \n                       |                                        |   ------------------------------  \n                       |                                        |   Ctrl+E Eingabe  Ctrl+W Kanal    \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nendpoint=http://localhost:5000 auth=session_env focus=navigation mode=normal Hub nicht erreichbar...\n \nCommands: :refresh :section <id>  [Ctrl+W] Focus/Kanal  [Ctrl+J/Ctrl+K] Move  [Ctrl+R] Refresh  [...\n"]
